displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: On Top by Karan Aujla has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. Never Fold is the highest at #10.
Shohrat by Jordan Sandhu and Chet Singh is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 50 spots at #15.
Jameson by Pavitar Lassoi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #37.
